parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFlOp.I told you, Mother. It’s the females of the species that are worth saving.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlHuAg.Argh! Get that thing out of my face!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.That holy relic is a good weapon against demons. If they come back, I’ll use it on them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlEx.If those monsters come back, I know how to defeat them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Come on, 1Hero. Let’s get the hell out of here!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoCl.Should we go find Brian? He can kill these things, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnEx^.I hate to be the bearer of bad news, but you people died and you came to Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnEx^.Listen! I’m not going to argue with you. You sucked at life, you died, and now you’re here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx>.He’s telling the truth. We came through a portal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlDe^.Haha! What a kooky bunch. The girls are going to love you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Listen here, monster. We are here for Erica. She committed blasphemy and she should be here…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnDe^.There are about 14 million Ericas here. Can you be more specific?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Lilith told us to meet her here at this altar.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvWoDe^.Lilith?... Did I come here on the wrong day?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElBaDe.You didn’t see a dark-skinned, pretty girl with short hair?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlDe^.Give me a moment. I need to speak with the manager.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Where is Erica? Are we in the right place?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe.I hope Brian doesn't drag his feet. We could use his help here too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Be on the lookout. Demons could show up at any moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnAg.If any more demons show up, I’ll cut their heads off!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdWoDe.Do you think the priest will find the Toma?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaDe.Are we sure we’re in the right place?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoCl^.Where is Lillian? What’s taking her so long?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.The angel was right… I guess this is real.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Everything’s fine. We just need Lillian to show up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.How many of you guys are looking for me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaEx.We’ve got a big party down here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Brian and the treasure hunters are looking for the Toma Leolo. We think it’s here in Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFrEx^.Lillian has your body… We’re just waiting on it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Erica… She’s in battle against another demon…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx^.Don’t worry. You didn’t commit blasphemy in vain. We’ll get your body back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We need to trust Lillian. She’ll do the right thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.That’s a lot of faith put into a demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I know she wants to save Erica… She cares about her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrOp.If you trust her, then I will too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx^.I’m going to send my men back into the mansion…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaDe^.We need to know if it’s safe to return.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe^.We know… But what else can we do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.He’s right. If things go south, we need to know how to escape.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.No… Trust me on that one. It’s not simple, getting in and out of the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.What’s with the priest? Is he back yet?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll check on Father Solomon. Wait here for Lillian.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlEx^.If those monsters come back, I know how to defeat them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrOp.Yeah… They can’t stand the holy relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.What’s with the priest? Is he back yet?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.We need to figure out how to escape through the mansion safely.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This ground looks weak. I wonder what would happen if I hit it with a pickaxe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx^.We don’t know how to get her back into her body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.I have no idea what I’m doing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx^.Do we need to say a prayer?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.What is Lillian’s plan? Is she bringing the Toma to us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoCl.What are you doing here?... And what are you holding?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx^.I have the Toma Leolo! I’m here to help you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp.You have the Toma? Where is Lillian?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx^.She’s distracting Daemalius… The Toma Leolo was never in that box.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx.Evie… How do we put a soul back into a body?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvHaEx.Welcome to Hell… Hopefully, your stay will be short.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoCl.The sooner we can get out of here, the better.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx.Come on, witch. Let’s get you back into that body of yours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.We don’t have time to play around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnEx^.Look… I know what I’m doing. Spank that body, girl!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaEx.We just have to bless the Toma while Erica holds it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFrEx.Here you go, girl. It’s all yours… Don’t let it come uncovered.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Hold still… I’m going to splash you and the rock with some holy water…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoCl.Fuck… What do we do now, Evie?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DmFlOp.Afraid, humans?... You’ll be my first victims.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaEx.I don’t know… Do you think my skinny ass would be a good warrior for your crusade?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DmFlEx.With the power of a demon’s soul, even a weakling such as you can be mighty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrHaCl.That sounds kinda cool. Can I go first?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.Uhh… Yeah… I’d love for you to… shove a demon into me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvWoCl.You better put some muscle into it, girl.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaEx.Howdy, Father! I just stuck a gold dildo into that demon’s ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Get out of here! I’ll hold him in place!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DmMaAg!c.I will kill you! You will be trapped in Hell for all eternity!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoCl^.Wait… You left! I saw you leave!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlDe.Looks like someone found a way back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Arianna… She opened a new portal… I’m here to rescue you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaAg.Hot damn! I thought I’d be trapped down here forever.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvFlEx.An ironic fate for a man of God… Too bad butter fingers over here caused all this mess.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx^.Hey! I slipped up. That bomb didn’t come with clear instructions.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.He has bigger fish to fry now… We’ve screwed over his plan pretty thoroughly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.But… Henry… How did you survive the explosion? You were the one who set off the bomb, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EvAnEx.Take a wild guess why Daemalius isn’t taking his revenge on butter fingers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Seems Henry here was a bit too naughty in life.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaEx^.What’s done is done… We need to get Father Solomon out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.I can hold my own against demons, but I’d rather not push my luck.");
